  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL22">
<l>pēciṟṟē pēca lallāṟ perumaiyoṉ ṟuṇara lākā</l>
<l>tācaṟṟār taṅkaṭ kallā laṟiyalā vāṉu mallaṉ</l>
<l>mācaṟṟār maṉattu ḷāṉai vaṇaṅkinā miruppa tallāl</l>
<l>pēcattā ṉāva tuṇṭō pētaineñ cēnī collāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Other than saying [again] what has been said,</l>
<l>it is not possible to understand any [of His] greatness.</l>
<l>He is not One who can be known, except to the faultless people.</l>
<l>O ignorant heart, you tell [me]! Other than our continuing to bow to Him</l>
<l>who is in the heart of the blemishless people, can [we] speak [of Him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
